Package ElectronicAssetTradingPlatform.AssetTrading

Class BuyOfferData

java.lang.Object
ElectronicAssetTradingPlatform.AssetTrading.OfferData
ElectronicAssetTradingPlatform.AssetTrading.BuyOfferData
public class BuyOfferData
extends OfferData
Retrieves and inserts data relating to buy offers to/from the database via network. Also contains methods which operate on the data retrieved from the database Singleton class
